msgstr ""

#: ../../../driver-api/80211/cfg80211:48: ../include/net/cfg80211.h:4741
msgid "``change_station``"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../driver-api/80211/cfg80211:48: ../include/net/cfg80211.h:4742
msgid ""
"Modify a given station. Note that flags changes are not much validated in "
"cfg80211, in particular the auth/assoc/authorized flags might come to the "
"driver in invalid combinations -- make sure to check them, also against the "
"existing state! Drivers must call cfg80211_check_station_change() to "
"validate the information."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../driver-api/80211/cfg80211:48: ../include/net/cfg80211.h:4746
