msgstr ""

#: ../../../driver-api/80211/cfg80211:170: ../include/net/cfg80211.h:8664
msgid ""
"Test mode is a set of utility functions to allow drivers to interact with "
"driver-specific tools to aid, for instance, factory programming."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../driver-api/80211/cfg80211:170: ../include/net/cfg80211.h:8668
msgid ""
"This chapter describes how drivers interact with it. For more information "
"see the nl80211 book's chapter on it."
